<% content_for :title do %> - Status<% end %>
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "pages" %>

<div id="status-titler">
	<div class="container">
		<%= image_tag("pages/SegoeUI-Graph.png") %>
		<div id="title">Carpe Status</div>
		<div id="sub-title">Since we're in active development, our features aren't all done. Here's a quick guide to our progress.</div>
		<div id="small-text">
			Interested in following along as we build Carpe?
			<a href="http://carpe-dev.tumblr.com/">Visit our development blog!</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div id="tiles-container" class="container">
	<div class="status-tile">
		<div class="image-container">
			<%= image_tag("pages/JustTheLetter.png") %>
		</div>
		<div class="tile-title">Carpe</div>
		<div class="tile-status alpha">Alpha</div>
		<div class="tile-text">
		The core components of the Carpe platform have been created, including basic scheduling with multiple views, unique social 
		features, and adaptive privacy settings. However, there is plenty more work to do on the functionality that will make Carpe 
		truly stand stand out, and some current features are still fairly unstable.
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="status-tile">
		<div class="image-container">
			<%= image_tag("pages/SegoeUI-Cal.png") %>
		</div>
		<div class="tile-title">Monthly View</div>
		<div class="tile-status alpha">Alpha</div>
		<div class="tile-text">
		Monthly view has been visually formatted (with some bugs), but is read-only at the moment and is thus in the Alpha state.
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="status-tile">
		<div class="image-container">
			<%= image_tag("pages/SegoeUI-People-Fuchsia.png") %>
		</div>
		<div class="tile-title">Group Scheduling</div>
		<div class="tile-status dev">Pre-Alpha</div>
		<div class="tile-text">
		User Groups are being worked on in the background, have not yet been released. Keep an eye our for news coming soon!
		</div>
	</div>
</div>